=== Alternative spellings===
'''sickle cell anemia'''

===Noun phrase===
'''sickle cell anaemia'''

# {{pathology}} A severe hereditary form of [[anaemia]], mainly [[affect]]ing [[people]] of [[Africa]]n [[origin]], in which mutated [[haemoglobin]] distorts [[red blood cell]]s
into a crescent shape, causing the cells to become stuck in [[capillary|capillaries]].
Downstream tissues are thus deprived of [[oxygen]] causing [[ischaemia]] and 
[[infarction]].

====Synonyms====
*[[drepanocytosis]]

